596
00:22:53,541 --> 00:22:54,500
And everything's going great

597
00:22:54,583 --> 00:22:56,166
until they bring out the soup.

598
00:22:56,250 --> 00:22:58,041
There's always a little bit
that splashes up, right?

599
00:22:58,125 --> 00:23:00,250
Well, doesn't it suck when
a drop gets on your clothes?

600
00:23:00,333 --> 00:23:02,333
And if it's curry sauce
it sucks even worse!

601
00:23:02,416 --> 00:23:03,958
Doesn't it seem like
it always happens

602
00:23:04,041 --> 00:23:05,583
when you're wearing
your favorite outfit?

603
00:23:05,666 --> 00:23:06,958
And then it's like,
you're totally bummed

604
00:23:07,041 --> 00:23:08,291
for the rest of
the day, you know?

605
00:23:08,375 --> 00:23:09,583
It's like when you buy
a bento box

606
00:23:09,666 --> 00:23:11,125
with soup at the store.

607
00:23:11,208 --> 00:23:12,875
You make sure to walk home
all steady and careful,

608
00:23:12,958 --> 00:23:14,625
keeping that bag level so
nothing spills out, right?

609
00:23:14,708 --> 00:23:17,291
Yeah. But then you get
home and you open the bag

610
00:23:17,375 --> 00:23:19,375
and the soup spilled out
and everything's soaked,

611
00:23:19,458 --> 00:23:20,916
and you're like,
"I'm so not hungry anymore."

612
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:23,416
And you know how nice it is when
they're bagging your stuff

613
00:23:23,500 --> 00:23:25,583
and they bother to separate
