614
00:23:25,666 --> 00:23:28,333
And then they screw it all up by
putting the magazines you bought

615
00:23:28,416 --> 00:23:30,000
in the same damn bag as
all your cold drinks.

616
00:23:30,083 --> 00:23:32,125
And then the paper soaks up
all the condensation!

617
00:23:32,208 --> 00:23:34,916
And now, you've got these
warped and soggy magazines.

618
00:23:35,000 --> 00:23:36,333
And you're thinking,

619
00:23:36,416 --> 00:23:37,750
"Why the hell did
they separate anything

620
00:23:37,833 --> 00:23:39,375
in the first place?"
You know?

621
00:23:39,458 --> 00:23:40,458
[sighs]

622
00:23:40,541 --> 00:23:41,708
Next episode,

623
00:23:41,791 --> 00:23:44,041
"Various Ways
